author: COMSOL
description:
This app demonstrates:

â€¢ Light theme

This app allows you to evaluate cross-section data for a wide range of American and European standard beams. Given a set of forces and moments acting on the section, you can also compute a detailed stress distribution.

Calculated cross-section data can also easily be extracted for use as input data for beam analyses in COMSOL Multiphysics.
label: beam_section_calculator.mph
